      <h4><b>Summer Time Oatmeal</b></h4>
      
      <div class="text-left">
<p class="title"><b>INGREDIENTS:</b></p>
<p class="title">1 Serving</p>
   <p>
      <li>3 Tbsp oats</li>
      <li>1 Cup (250 ml) milk or water</li>
      <li>1 Tsp grape molasses</li>
      <li>1 Tsp flaxseeds</li>
      <li>Half a handful of spinach</li>
      <li>2 Dates</li>
      <li>5 Raw Hazelnuts</li>
      <li>1 Peach</li>
      <li>7 Mulberries</li>
  </p>
