      <p class="title"><b>PREPARATION:</b></p>
      <li><b>1.</b> Add 3 tbsp oat to half a cup of (125 ml) milk or water and let it sit overnight in the fridge.</li>
      <li><b>2.</b> Next day, put the oats, half a cup of (125ml) milk/water, molasses, flaxseed, spinach, half a peach and dates in a blender then blend.</li>
      <li><b>3.</b> Take the mixture on the serving plate. (You can add more milk or water according to its consistency).</li>
      <li><b>4.</b> Garnish with a chopped half peach, hazelnuts and mulberries then serve.</li>
    
